---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Riley Miller">
  <div class="py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl mb-16">About</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none
      prose-headings:text-[var(--text-primary)] prose-headings:font-normal
      prose-p:text-[var(--text-secondary)]
      prose-a:text-[var(--text-primary)] prose-a:underline hover:prose-a:no-underline
      prose-strong:text-[var(--text-primary)]
      prose-ul:text-[var(--text-secondary)]
      prose-li:text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
      
      <p>
        Hi! I'm Riley Miller, a software engineer passionate about building great products and solving complex problems.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Currently, I'm a Senior Software Engineer at Resend, where I focus on building developer tools and infrastructure. 
        Previously, I've worked at companies like Temporal, PlanSource, and others, contributing to distributed systems, 
        cloud infrastructure, and developer experience improvements.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        This site serves as my personal space on the web where I share my thoughts on software development, 
        technology trends, and my journey in tech. I believe in continuous learning and enjoy exploring new 
        technologies and methodologies.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Senior Software Engineer</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">Resend • 2023 - Present</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Building developer tools and infrastructure for modern email delivery</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Software Engineer</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">Temporal • 2022 - 2023</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Worked on distributed systems and workflow orchestration platform</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Software Engineer</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">PlanSource • 2021 - 2022</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Developed benefits administration platform and improved developer experience</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Technical Interests</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Web Development (React, TypeScript, Node.js)</li>
        <li>Cloud Architecture and DevOps</li>
        <li>Performance Optimization</li>
        <li>Open Source Software</li>
        <li>Developer Tools and Productivity</li>
      </ul>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>